    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165350/extras/58e9899f37fcbff57ccd50a1e2b14ca7.avif?t=1667030671\" width=596 height=326 /></span>.<br>Lazerhawk是一款赛车游戏，灵感来自80年代末和90年代初的视觉效果，音乐，游戏和汽车。它建立在自定义游戏引擎之上，<br>具有真实的复古感和独特的图形。您将首先从一辆车开始，然后您将能够升级它或用钱购买其他汽车<br>在每次运行结束时获得。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165350/extras/a9dd98260b8aa61cf0645f328fe6fc5b.poster.avif?t=1667030671\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165350/extras/a9dd98260b8aa61cf0645f328fe6fc5b.webm?t=1667030671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165350/extras/a9dd98260b8aa61cf0645f328fe6fc5b.mp4?t=1667030671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br>通过不同的独特级别赛车！<br>注意路上的其他车辆。玩这个游戏是一个具有挑战性和令人兴奋的体验。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165350/extras/e89cb3a6b90b4eebf2ae44034656c4ab.poster.avif?t=1667030671\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165350/extras/e89cb3a6b90b4eebf2ae44034656c4ab.webm?t=1667030671\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165350/extras/e89cb3a6b90b4eebf2ae44034656c4ab.mp4?t=1667030671\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br>特征：<br><br>■ 不少于8辆车。<br>■ 超过3个不同的级别。<br>■ 4种不同的游戏模式。<br>■ 正确的评分系统。<br>■ 购车系统性能升级.<br>■ 新颜色和车轮的采购系统。<br>■ 无尽的高速公路.",
